text: Minnesota Senate, District 20 is a district of the Minnesota Senate which covers a majority of Rice County, all of Le Sueur County, and part of Scott County in southeastern Minnesota. == Elections == == Senators == Rich Draheim (January 3, 2017 – present) Kevin Dahle (January 8, 2013 - January 2, 2017) == References == * Category:Minnesota legislative districts Category:Rice County, Minnesota Category:Le Sueur County, Minnesota Category:Scott County, Minnesota
title: Minnesota Senate, District 20
